---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const inquiryHref = 'https://circularaction.org/ca-reimbursements';
---

<BaseLayout title="SB 54 in California" description="A starting point for what's ahead under SB 54 and how to get involved.">
  <div class="landing">
    <section class="landing__hero">
      <p class="landing__eyebrow">Welcome</p>
      <h1>This is your starting point for what's ahead under&nbsp;SB&nbsp;54 and how you can get involved.</h1>
      <p class="landing__lede">
        California's recycling and reuse system is evolving. In the coming years, SB&nbsp;54 will be driving real improvements in how single-use packaging and food service ware is collected, processed, and returned to use — creating a more consistent, connected system statewide.
      </p>
      <p class="landing__lede">
        Whether you've already connected with CAA or are learning about CAA for the first time, this page is designed to help you understand what's coming next and how you can begin to engage.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="landing-card">
      <h2 class="landing-card__title">Get Started</h2>
      <p>CAA is working with local service providers across the system, including:</p>
      <ul class="landing-card__list">
        <li>Local Jurisdictions</li>
        <li>Tribes</li>
        <li>Community Based Organizations</li>
        <li>Haulers</li>
        <li>MRFs</li>
        <li>Transfer Stations</li>
        <li>Compost Facilities</li>
        <li>Alternative Collection Providers</li>
        <li>End Markets</li>
        <li>Reuse Programs</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        Outreach is ongoing, but you don't have to wait to get involved. If you want to explore reimbursement opportunities or next steps, connect with CAA.
      </p>
      <a href={inquiryHref} class="btn btn--primary">Get in touch <span class="btn__icon" aria-hidden="true">👉</span></a>
    </section>

    <aside class="landing__note">
      <h2 class="landing__note-title">Learn More</h2>
      <p>More information is coming soon to this site.</p>
    </aside>

    {/*
      Reserved for when FAQs are ready:

      <section>
        <h2>Want a clearer view of what's ahead?</h2>
        <a href="/questions/">Explore what's coming (FAQs)</a>
      </section>
    */}
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .landing {
    max-width: calc(var(--content-width) + var(--sidebar-width) + var(--space-2xl));
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .landing__hero {
    padding: var(--space-3xl) 0 var(--space-2xl);
    border-bottom: 3px solid var(--caa-teal);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl);
    max-width: var(--max-line-length);
  }

  .landing__eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--caa-teal);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .landing__lede {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: var(--caa-navy);
    max-width: var(--max-line-length);
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  .landing-card {
    max-width: var(--max-line-length);
    border: 1px solid rgba(33, 140, 165, 0.18);
    border-radius: var(--card-radius);
    padding: var(--space-xl);
    background: var(--caa-paper);
    box-shadow: var(--card-shadow);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }

  .landing-card__title {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--caa-navy);
  }

  .landing-card p {
    margin: 0;
  }

  .landing-card__list {
    margin: 0;
    padding-left: var(--space-lg);
    color: var(--caa-ink);
  }

  .landing-card__list li {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.4em;
    align-self: flex-start;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: var(--space-sm) var(--space-lg);
    border-radius: 4px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background 0.15s, color 0.15s;
    margin-top: auto;
  }

  .btn--primary {
    background: var(--caa-yellow);
    color: var(--caa-navy);
  }

  .btn--primary:hover {
    background: var(--caa-navy);
    color: var(--caa-paper);
  }

  .btn__icon {
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .landing__note {
    max-width: var(--max-line-length);
    padding: var(--space-lg) 0;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(11, 54, 71, 0.1);
  }

  .landing__note-title {
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-xs);
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--caa-navy);
  }

  .landing__note p {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--caa-ink);
    opacity: 0.75;
  }
</style>
